# Yeni Permission Prosedürü

## Step 1: Permission Tanımı

`packages/policy/permissions.ts` — `resource:action` format, MVP enum'a ekle.

## Step 2: Role Map

`packages/policy/role-permission-map.ts` — `Docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` yetki matrisi ile birebir.

## Step 3: ABAC (Gerekirse)

`packages/policy/abac-rules.ts` — company/assignment/clearance koşulu.

## Step 4: Field Visibility (Gerekirse)

`packages/policy/field-visibility-defaults.ts` — yeni alan masking kuralları.

## Step 5: Backend Enforcement

- `@RequirePolicy('new:permission')` endpoint'lerde
- PolicyGuard integration test: pozitif + negatif her rol

## Step 6: Frontend UX

`usePermissions()` + `<PermissionGate>` — yalnızca UX.

## Step 7: Seed

Test kullanıcıları her rol için permission set ile seed/factory güncelle.

## Step 8: Dokümantasyon

- [ ] `Docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` matris güncellendi
- [ ] `Docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` endpoint permission sütunu

